# Analog and Digital Representation

- After [[61-Archive/20220311115526-sensors|Sensors]] detects the signal, it has to be represented and stored somewhere

![../60-Meta-Attachments/cb9b6f4891e606d5da5291ba00635d68.png](data:image/png;base64,)

| Analog                      | Digital                       |
| --------------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| Store as voltage or current | sotred as pulse or numbers    |
| continuous values           | Discrete values               |
| Higher accuracy             | Some data loss                |
|                             | easier to store and duplicate |

- [[61-Archive/20220311124439-data-sampling|Data Sampling]] converts analog to digital
